results.title: Custom word ring, handmade ring with personalized text, adjustable ring, lettering ( love, peace, hope ring and so on)
results.description:
Handmade wire ring with your favourite word!

This listing is for 1 -made to order- ring. Every ring is adjustable and made of aluminium. You can choose between 9 colors: silver, browny, pink, blue, black, light blue, red, orange or green. 

You can choose between a wide range of words. If you want a word which isn't in the list, choose ''custom word'' and then write me the word in a message. You can choose any word from 1 to 5 letters. 
Please note that the 5 letters words fit better with medium-large size rings.
You can also choose 5-6-7 letters words, considering that the letters will wrap around your finger.
New: now also available in the heart shape! Check it out in the second picture.

If you purchase more than one ring, you can create sweet sentences: for example in the pictures I show the live-laugh-love combination, or peace and love, love you, you and me and so on. 

Please notify me in the note if you want uppercase letters or initials.

All rings are adjustable, and start from a medium size (8). If you need it smaller, or larger than size 10, write me your size in a message. You can write me your approx size, where small starts from 6,5 / 7, and large starts from 10 (us size)

Each ring is totally handmade, that's why no piece can be identical to the other - but all are made with the same commitment and care.

*Purchase now and take advantage of the promotion! A free gift with every order of more than 5 € !*
